                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-8">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h5 class="card-title"><a target="_blank" href="https://www.ets.org/gre/test-takers/general-test/prepare/prep-books-services.html"><b>Official ETS Book</b></a></h5>
                                    <p class="card-text">
                                        Official book from ETS, the maker of the GRE General Test. Contains hundreds of authentic GRE test questions, explanations, test-taking strategies, sample essay responses and more.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
